Awp_redo_final

By: Redo

This is a smaller AWP map, meant to realistically emulate standard map distances and cover moreso than most awp maps out there. It has turned out to be a great map for warmup prior to scrims/matches, and may even have some tourny value. Not designed for big games (12+ players), but still may be excellent for big games. Very cozy for 2-8 players.
